com.explodingbacon.bcnlib.framework

Class ExtendableRobot

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.RobotBase
      • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.IterativeRobot
        • com.explodingbacon.bcnlib.framework.ExtendableRobot

  • public abstract class ExtendableRobot
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.IterativeRobot
    The main class of the robot. This takes care of creating, initializing, and running all other classes. MAKE SURE you call super when you override a method, or else the entire framework will break.
